{"tid":1497500,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[823人鏈]如果唔夠人，可以拎長遮！","createTime":"2019-08-23T03:54:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T06:53:52.000Z","uid":290313,"like":32,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"438898488548373faf691c6d46da490db4a7d77e","tid":1497500,"uid":290313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T03:54:12.000Z","msg":"關於今晚組人鏈，最多人關心係以下兩個問題：<br />\n<br />\n一：驚唔夠人<br />\n二：陌生人拖手好尷尬<br />\n<br />\n其實只要一個方法應該可以幫手拆掂上面呢兩個問題！<br />\n<br />\n我見公海谷出左呢張文宣，叫大家拎啲野出黎，就唔洗直接掂人隻手咁尷<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JhfRXL7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJhfRXL7.jpg&h=68105147&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實大家拎返發夢工具之一<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">長遮</span></span>唔係更加好咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n<br />\n如果用長遮既話，一黎唔洗直接掂手，<br />\n二黎可以幫手延長條人鏈(少少都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)，<br />\n三黎長遮係以往呢兩個月既抗爭活動必備，出現都好合理<br />\n四黎今次係和理非活動，但手上拎埋發夢必備品，又可以象徵<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">和勇合一</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然其他物品例如<span style=\"color: purple;\">眼罩、頭盔</span>都係唔錯既選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1338a79cc8022c670d45631cb96fb1156f9f955e","tid":1497500,"uid":273252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T03:55:25.000Z","msg":"要大肆宣傳set 一個deadline.<br />\n講明<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>若果deadline前政府都唔回應五大訴求, 會行動升級</strong></span> 後果自負<br />\n<br />\n用意: 先小人後君子<br />\n1)迫使政府回應<br />\n2)市民有心理準備當日會有行動<br />\n3)令市民知道當天有行動係源於政府唔回應 <br />\n    (令佢地明白若果政府肯回應就唔會有行動阻礙到佢番工, 出街)<br />\n<br />\n<strong>1) 五大訴求</strong><br />\n一、徹底撤回修例<br />\n二、收回暴動定義<br />\n三、撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況, 解散、追究及重組警隊<br />\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選<br />\n<br />\n[下一步棋] 救香港 Set Deadline 行動升級 (幫推)<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1497453\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1497453</a>"},{"pid":"3ac94abfd09874f690f7fa4aec445cca0fd6a181","tid":1497500,"uid":228337,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T04:10:46.000Z","msg":"我相信香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今晚一定要出嚟呀你老味<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<code>823人鏈 824機場觀塘 825荃葵青</code>"},{"pid":"0429ad77e64bf93a216641939ee9819c4d8f2dae","tid":1497500,"uid":212274,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T04:14:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f98d96584064f889683ed4cab44097f93cfda92f","tid":1497500,"uid":140117,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T04:16:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8d2de4523feeeb7042a757d4854bea58111ce07b","tid":1497500,"uid":91866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T04:27:05.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9249243c3735c391f934ae6b98eefbf65fb44d0d","tid":1497500,"uid":284529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T04:29:22.000Z","msg":"「8.23香港之路」集合點出席人數估算<br />\n<br />\n1. 已報名人士請準時七點出席。 <br />\n2. 統計結果只供事前參考，實際落場未必有相同人數，請睇嘅手足請自行決定，亦請相信香港人集體智慧。<br />\n3. Google Form將於下午5時前停止更新 <br />\n4. 現場最新消息將以TG channel 及 FB 為準<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdn8obEeNEp4bN-uOJ95qL1tckBql7WIJ5poZR6Xa4BF9hG8w/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSdn8obEeNEp4bN-uOJ95qL1tckBql7WIJ5poZR6Xa4BF9hG8w%2Fviewform&d=d0UHt22HnArKS4Vgrvpv1Sq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=f0ddff38\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdn8obEeNEp4bN-uOJ95qL1tckBql7WIJ5poZR6Xa4BF9hG8w/viewform</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">就算唔報名都可以參與 , 到時直接去集合點就OK , 不過幫手登記可以方便統計人數 同 分配人流<br />\n<br />\n已有3萬8千多人登記參與 , 登記無須填寫個人資料 , 可以參考統計結果選擇去未滿人既集合點<br />\n<br />\n現時 荃灣,旺角,觀塘,中環 都超級爆人 , 有心人可考慮其他集合點 , 多謝</span></span>"},{"pid":"3a5bf386c18fe93dfdec5bed5399a8e7003ea3c8","tid":1497500,"uid":13514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T04:45:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cffb10bb6ad2db46ee0d2a81c16802bbd61847b","tid":1497500,"uid":854,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T04:52:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">石峽尾 樂富 大窩口 油塘 牛頭角 鰂魚涌 荔枝角 西營盤 紅磡 全部都要人呀</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">ocamp搞手可唔可以帶啲願意join嘅fm去拖下手仔？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"e06a63c377ea61ff6fc6c35e77781c4e0f35ad1f","tid":1497500,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T04:53:09.000Z","msg":"ok"},{"pid":"5a1f9b12bacb589f42c043da6fab94186b0dee14","tid":1497500,"uid":268160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T04:56:15.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"bff363b94606383f408244784a555f957804531b","tid":1497500,"uid":11071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T04:56:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"29a6415a859850f24dd821fb7b0ae364633ba7ed","tid":1497500,"uid":290313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1cffb10bb6ad2db46ee0d2a81c16802bbd61847b","tid":1497500,"uid":854,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T04:52:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">石峽尾 樂富 大窩口 油塘 牛頭角 鰂魚涌 荔枝角 西營盤 紅磡 全部都要人呀</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">ocamp搞手可唔可以帶啲願意join嘅fm去拖下手仔？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>